                                "stop": 9.584,
                                "byte_start": 92067,
                                "byte_stop": 130415,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in Watkins against Sowders and Summitt against Sowders will be announced by Justice Stewart."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 9.584,
                        "stop": 68.824,
